name: Men's 'Valkyrie' Flight Jacket
description: A rare item that can sometimes be found in the black markets and underworld bazaars of New Eden, this jacket shows that the wearer is a follower of the mysterious Valkyrie. Crafted from the finest leather in a two-tone pattern reflecting the Valkyrie colors, the jacket is emblazoned with the logo of this renegade fighter pilot group over the heart of the proud wearer.
